A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Washington County – Property Tax Credit for Disabled Veterans – Eligibility
3 FOR the purpose of expanding eligibility for a certain property tax credit in Washington
4 County for certain disabled veterans to include certain members of the National
5 Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration and the Public Health Service; and
6 generally relating to a property tax credit for disabled veterans in Washington
7 County.
